data.description: Nestled in the heart of a vibrant and growing community, this charming residence offers an ideal blend of comfort and convenience. The property boasts a well-designed layout featuring three bedrooms, two bathrooms, two spacious living rooms, and a delightful inground pool. Upon entering, you are greeted by a foyer that leads into the main living area. The first living room serves as a welcoming space for gatherings. The second living room offers versatility, perhaps as a cozy den or a playroom.  Both living spaces are thoughtfully designed with neutral tones, creating a serene ambiance. Flex space that could be used as a 4th bedroom or private home office and an additional half bath located in pool house. The highlight of the backyard is a sparkling inground pool, perfect for relaxation and entertaining guests on warm days. A paved patio area provides an excellent space for outdoor dining and lounging.
